Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing’ game
MADISON, Wis. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Wisconsin Lottery’s “All or Nothing” game were:
02-05-06-07-08-10-11-13-18-19-22
(two, five, six, seven, eight, ten, eleven, thirteen, eighteen, nineteen, twenty-two)
